    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/0f4d391e9aca119551ed5dc916c64899.avif?t=1754021116\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras_big/0f4d391e9aca119551ed5dc916c64899.avif?t=1754021116 width=800 height=83 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>《人格解体》是一款基于克苏鲁神话世界观创作的角色扮演游戏。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/05647d9183b90cf63875ed855f412479.webp?t=1754021116\" width=17 height=17 /></span>  在游戏中，你将置身于一座超脱时间洪流之外的时空图书馆。作为犹格索托斯的造物与祂意志的寄托——星之钥，你将代祂跨越穷极之门，前往各个世界修补破碎的时空。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/05647d9183b90cf63875ed855f412479.webp?t=1754021116\" width=17 height=17 /></span>  目前游戏已成功推出了4个探索类模组、1个文字模组、1个规则模组，以及备受期待的大型模组《卡森德拉的黑色嘉年华》，游戏文本总量已累积至66万字。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/968cd45c372715126e52f046a7ea1ebd.avif?t=1754021116\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras_big/968cd45c372715126e52f046a7ea1ebd.avif?t=1754021116 width=800 height=231 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/05647d9183b90cf63875ed855f412479.webp?t=1754021116\" width=17 height=17 /></span>  而且游戏主界面设有创作模式，玩家可以使用编辑器创建并发布原创模组。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/b1eea734819a8599b47a5d8b426082c5.avif?t=1754021116\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras_big/b1eea734819a8599b47a5d8b426082c5.avif?t=1754021116 width=800 height=83 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>这是一个具有克苏鲁跑团味道的游戏</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/05647d9183b90cf63875ed855f412479.webp?t=1754021116\" width=17 height=17 /></span>  在各个模组中，你将作为一名调查员，需要收集线索、掷骰判定、触发剧情、逐步接近(或远离)事情的真相。如果你是新手玩家,《人格解体》可以帮你快速熟悉跑团流程，体验到独特的随机性乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/05647d9183b90cf63875ed855f412479.webp?t=1754021116\" width=17 height=17 /></span>  我们的故事灵感来源于克苏鲁神话，可能怪诞惊悚、猎奇吊诡，但不完全是为了带来恐惧体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/57c93ccc92666761f2d018c718c229a7.poster.avif?t=1754021116\" width=800 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/57c93ccc92666761f2d018c718c229a7.webm?t=1754021116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/57c93ccc92666761f2d018c718c229a7.mp4?t=1754021116\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/33826e1ceeb7249ef45b85beb4ae015b.avif?t=1754021116\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras_big/33826e1ceeb7249ef45b85beb4ae015b.avif?t=1754021116 width=800 height=83 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>为了获取真相，有时或许…可以不择手段?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/05647d9183b90cf63875ed855f412479.webp?t=1754021116\" width=17 height=17 /></span>  你可以贿赂，偷窃，交易，安抚故事中的角色，采取的不同行动将造成不同的剧情走向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/05647d9183b90cf63875ed855f412479.webp?t=1754021116\" width=17 height=17 /></span>  获胜方式为什么一定要战斗？试试隐匿，对目标一击毙命，也可以通过恐吓让目标逃走。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/05647d9183b90cf63875ed855f412479.webp?t=1754021116\" width=17 height=17 /></span>  如果你获得一些禁忌的知识，魔法将会是克敌制胜的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      (但或许会有额外的副作用嗬~=`の'，请谨慎使用)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/40ba71be5328c8b5f0768f87cf5fe2b8.avif?t=1754021116\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras_big/40ba71be5328c8b5f0768f87cf5fe2b8.avif?t=1754021116 width=800 height=83 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>这是一个主打收集要素的游戏</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/05647d9183b90cf63875ed855f412479.webp?t=1754021116\" width=17 height=17 /></span>  我们的收集内容涵盖了模组结局、角色特质、法术、伙伴以及神话物品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/05647d9183b90cf63875ed855f412479.webp?t=1754021116\" width=17 height=17 /></span>  在模组中探索禁忌知识，将使你的调查员角色掌握施展法术的力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/c9a68523eb80cf218ecfa79c5912a180.poster.avif?t=1754021116\" width=800 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/c9a68523eb80cf218ecfa79c5912a180.webm?t=1754021116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/c9a68523eb80cf218ecfa79c5912a180.mp4?t=1754021116\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/05647d9183b90cf63875ed855f412479.webp?t=1754021116\" width=17 height=17 /></span>  在故事中，你将邂逅众多新角色，解锁他们的独特剧情。随着故事的发展，他们将成为你并肩作战的伙伴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/af0cf127141b4c612e61d83ba492a99c.poster.avif?t=1754021116\" width=800 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/af0cf127141b4c612e61d83ba492a99c.webm?t=1754021116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/af0cf127141b4c612e61d83ba492a99c.mp4?t=1754021116\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/05647d9183b90cf63875ed855f412479.webp?t=1754021116\" width=17 height=17 /></span>  此外，每个故事都隐藏着独特的神话物品。收集并巧妙运用这些物品，将为你的角色带来超乎寻常的能力提升。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/044106e7e0be4844a1eafb9e2aa5cb9e.poster.avif?t=1754021116\" width=800 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/044106e7e0be4844a1eafb9e2aa5cb9e.webm?t=1754021116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/044106e7e0be4844a1eafb9e2aa5cb9e.mp4?t=1754021116\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/05647d9183b90cf63875ed855f412479.webp?t=1754021116\" width=17 height=17 /></span>  每个模组都有着不同的结局，一旦你达成这些结局，你的所有角色便能继承这段经历，从而解锁该结局下独有的角色收集内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/7b780fb8c0e8e5e646eb0c9d46b75389.avif?t=1754021116\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras_big/7b780fb8c0e8e5e646eb0c9d46b75389.avif?t=1754021116 width=800 height=432 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/05647d9183b90cf63875ed855f412479.webp?t=1754021116\" width=17 height=17 /></span>  你的调查员角色将经历独一无二的冒险，这些经历将转化为特质，赋予角色特殊的能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/d921fda35e44f77bf738e72b9af3bcbe.avif?t=1754021116\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras_big/d921fda35e44f77bf738e72b9af3bcbe.avif?t=1754021116 width=800 height=432 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/c09ab74250150db794946e9fea6909d2.avif?t=1754021116\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras_big/c09ab74250150db794946e9fea6909d2.avif?t=1754021116 width=800 height=83 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>这还是一个故事创作平台</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/05647d9183b90cf63875ed855f412479.webp?t=1754021116\" width=17 height=17 /></span>  游戏中内置了强大的故事编辑器，让创作者能够自由创作游戏内的所有内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/05647d9183b90cf63875ed855f412479.webp?t=1754021116\" width=17 height=17 /></span>  如果你热爱文字创作，那么你可以利用编辑器打造视觉小说风格的文字模组。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/05647d9183b90cf63875ed855f412479.webp?t=1754021116\" width=17 height=17 /></span>  如果你擅长构建游戏机制，那么创作规则类型的模组将是你展现设计的绝佳方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/05647d9183b90cf63875ed855f412479.webp?t=1754021116\" width=17 height=17 /></span>  若你渴望创造一个更加自由、开放的游戏世界，那么探索模组的制作将满足你的这一愿望。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/05647d9183b90cf63875ed855f412479.webp?t=1754021116\" width=17 height=17 /></span>  目前创意工坊中已有可游玩模组50+，定期模组共创活动正长期进行中！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/4a465d3340e442a7a4b7bfe6d091410d.poster.avif?t=1754021116\" width=800 height=235 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1477070/extras/4a465d3340e442a7a4b7bfe6d091410d.webm?t=1754021116\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
